episodes.title: Emails reveal what REALLY happened on Andrew’s final Epstein trip
episodes.description:
The New York trip that Andrew Mountbatten-Windsor insisted was only to “cut ties” with Jeffrey Epstein was, in fact, a five-day long weekend in which they met celebs including a Victoria’s Secret model. 

The former prince said he went only to tell the paedo financier that they could no longer be friends following Epstein’s conviction for soliciting a minor for prostitution. 

But damning documents released by US investigators suggested a packed itinerary with other guests including Latvian model Lana Zakocela, then 21. 

Epstein even hosted a lavish dinner at his £60million Manhattan home in Andrew’s honour.

episodes.title: Ghislaine Maxwell PACES in cell and SCOFFS prison food in grim CCTV released in Epstein files
episodes.description:
Footage from the Epstein files has revealed disgraced madame Ghislaine Maxwell's life inside her prison cell. 

The socialite was a close associate of the late paedophile Jeffrey Epstein, who died in jail in 2019.

The video shows Maxwell sporting an all-orange jumpsuit surrounded by white walls and a weathered grey floor.

After drinking a cup of water, Maxwell then tidies her bed before lying back, yawning, and resting with a book. 

The footage, filmed while she was awaiting a bail decision, also shows Maxwell scoffing prison food.
